posting_body: ['Contact info:', 'Mike Miller | The Apartment Resource |', 'show contact info', '1BR/1BA Apartment - Plymouth', 'Hwy 169, Plymouth, MN 55442', '$1,520/mo', 'KEY FEATURES', 'Sq Footage:', '788 sqft.', 'Bedrooms:', '1 Beds', 'Bathrooms:', '1 Baths', 'Parking:', '1 Dedicated', 'Lease Duration:', '1 Year', 'Deposit:', '$500', 'Pets Policy:', 'Cats & Dogs OK', 'Laundry:', 'In Unit', 'Property Type:', 'Apartment', 'DESCRIPTION', 'Offering spacious 1, 2 and 3 bedroom apartments in Plymouth, MN.', ' Located minutes to downtown Minneapolis and close to great shopping, dining entertainment, the busline and jogging trails.', 'Within the community is an outdoor pool, picnic & BBQ area, volleyball and tennis courts and underground garage parking.', 'We design features to fit any lifestyle.', "For a relaxing, comfortable lifestyle close to everything you need, yet removed from the hectic pace, it's time to come home.", 'Apartments include an in-home washer and dryer, patio or balcony, California closets, vaulted ceilings*, and so much more!', ' Prices and availability are subject to change.', ' Photos may not represent exact unit.', 'Call Mike to tour.', 'show contact info', 'RENTAL FEATURES', 'Living room', 'Dining room', 'Walk-in closet', 'Stove / Oven', 'Refrigerator', 'Dishwasher', 'Microwave', 'Balcony, Deck, or Patio', 'Central heat', 'Air conditioning', 'Cable-ready', 'High-speed internet', 'Hardwood floor', 'Tile floor', 'High / Vaulted ceiling', 'COMMUNITY FEATURES', 'Elevator', 'Secured entry', 'Shared pool', 'Clubhouse', 'Playground', 'Tennis court', 'Guest parking', 'Garage - Attached', 'LEASE TERMS', '12  Months', 'Contact info:', 'Mike Miller', 'The Apartment Resource', 'show contact info', 'Equal Housing Opportunity']
